❌ Where We Started Getting Stuck
1. TypeScript / NestJS Observable vs Promise Mismatch
Initial implementation called .pipe() on a Promise<UserResponse> instead of an Observable<UserResponse>.

This threw TS2339 errors until we explicitly returned an Observable from ClientGrpc and converted via firstValueFrom().

2. Metadata Parameter Type Errors
Attempted to pass Metadata directly where Nest expected (err, resp) => void callback, causing:

python
